message.content:
1. The Camino Verde community mobilisation intervention was effective in reducing dengue infections.
2. The Camino Verde community mobilisation intervention was effective in reducing household use of insecticide anti-mosquito products.
3. The Camino Verde community mobilisation intervention was effective in reducing household expenditure on insecticide anti-mosquito products.

messages.content:
Statement: The Camino Verde community mobilisation intervention, as well as being effective in reducing dengue infections, was effective in reducing household use of and expenditure on insecticide anti-mosquito products.
